dictionary.description: Though it did not result in an appointment to the role of Oracle Maiden, scholars have concluded that Rinon trained extensively in her homeland of Sacred Mt. Bari. In fact, she lived a life fit for a high-ranking cleric. Had she become Oracle Maiden, the same impressive abilities that made her a candidate might have also made her an ideal intermediary between humanity and the gods. Had she chosen not to participate in the war with the Holy Emperor, she certainly would have been a force for human salvation in the great Grand Gaian war that followed.
dictionary.evolution:
Maybe I was unprepared.
But I understand now. I understand my purpose.
dictionary.fusion:
Thank you.
I'm sure you're struggling too. Let's both give it our best!
dictionary.summon:
I was such a child then...
But just saying that makes me feel old.
